==English==
Function: noun

===Etymology===
Portuguese [[araribá]], from [[Tupi]]
===Noun===
#any of several trees of the genus ''[[Centrolobium]]'' (family [[Fabaceae]]); especially : a Brazilian tree (''[[Centrolobium robustum]]'') -- called also [[zebrawood]]
#any of several trees of the genus ''[[Sickingia]]'' usually with heavy dark red wood
#the wood of an arariba tree

